    "3D mapping measurements were performed on inVia™ confocal Raman microscope (Renishaw, United Kingdom) with 532 nm (6 mW, 10 s for each exposure).",
    "The map of one selected area (584 μm × 584 μm × 60 μm) was acquired with a resolution of 8 μm × 8 μm × 20 μm in X, Y, and Z.",
    "For measuring of I RS on silicon 10 -1 M of R6G aqueous solution was used.",
    "To accurately estimate the number of molecules excited by the confocal microscope, a ×20 objective lens with a 1.1 mm beam waist was illuminated through a container with a depth of 3 mm.",
